Author: alex-ant
Title: [BOUNTY] TravelChain BOUNTY CAMPAIGN. Make a trip of your dreams!
Body: Hello! There is a report form in the bottom of the bounty campaign topic. You need to submit your progress there.  Quote from: SL HE on November 15, 2017, 06:35:29 AM Hello. A few questions: In what ratio will the miles be exchanged for tokens? The specified number of miles per twitter activity takes into account one fact of activity or a week of activity? Where I can see a participants spreadsheet? Thank you for your answer.  Hello! Soon there will be a spreadsheet with the information about all of the miles earned by community and every participant will get a percent from the whole sum of tokens according to the number of miles earned during bounty campaign. Miles for the twitter activity are given each week. We will post a spreadsheet as soon as we form it basing on reports for each category of the campaign.
